skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
This is your local Flash Briefing to help you sell, buy, and rent Wenatchee real estate with your Wenatchee real estate agent Shannon Kraft. 

Shannon: "I have a servant’s heart and I love to help people. I have years of experience in the buying and selling process. My goal is to guide you through even the most complex real estate transactions with ease. Real Estate isn’t my job, it’s my passion! I specialize in putting the “Real” back in Real Estate."

This voice technology is provided by My Home Agent at HomeyPoints. Find out more about voice real estate marketing at www.HomeyPoints.com.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
